cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SY

The paper discusses a black box optimization algorithm for hyper parameter tuning of machine learning models, which falls under the category of machine learning and neural networks. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a parameterless optimization algorithm, which can be considered as a contribution to the field of optimization and search algorithms, falling under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper discusses the application of the proposed algorithm to deep learning models, which can be considered as a control and optimization problem, falling under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
